<h3 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h3>
<p>Another approach would be to let  <span class="process-math">\(u=\tan(x)\)</span> so that <span class="process-math">\(\text{,}\)</span> and <span class="process-math">\(\dx{u}=\sec^2(x)\dx{x}\text{.}\)</span> In that case we have</p>
<div class="displaymath process-math" data-contains-math-knowls="">
\begin{equation}
\int\tan(x)\dx{x}=\int\frac{u}{\sec^2(x)}\dx{u}=\int\frac{u}{1+\tan^2(x)}\dx{u}=\int\frac{u}{1+u^2}\dx{u}.\tag{1.1}
\end{equation}
</div>
<span class="incontext"><a href="section-4.html#p-60" class="internal">in-context</a></span>
</body>
